<plot>David Bigoney races in the dark. A documentary about a man who lost his sight and his family in a tragic, life changing moment. Years later, he is unwilling to allow his blindness to alter his life and his future. Through triathlons he has found a way to re-create an active lifestyle rich in competition and a sense of freedom. All the while inspiring so many around him.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?130186</url></doc>
